<title>USA: IPO FILING - Advantage Learning Systems.</title>
<headline>IPO FILING - Advantage Learning Systems.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-02-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Company Name  Advantage Learning Systems Inc</p>
<p> Stock symbol			    ALSI.O</p>
<p> Estimated price range	   $11-13/shr</p>
<p> Total shares to be offered    3.0 million</p>
<p> Shrs offered by company	 3.0 million</p>
<p> Lead Underwriter	 Piper Jaffray Inc</p>
<p>Underwriters over-allotment  450,000 shrs</p>
<p>Business: Wisconsin Rapids, Wis.,-based provider of learning information systems to kindergarten through senior high schools in the United States and Canada, including computer software and related training aimed at bolstering academic performance.</p>
<p>Use of Proceeds: Payment of undistributed S Corp earnings, repayment of certain debt, payment to company employees for certain benefits, and general corporate purposes, including working capital and new product development.</p>
